The '''Alien Combine''' was a [[Coruscanti/Legends|Coruscanti]] all-alien [[Anti-Humanism|anti-Human]] movement. It was founded in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. 

==History==
The Alien Combine originally worked through non-violent methods. However, when [[Evir Derricote]] began secretly capturing members as part of the [[Krytos virus|Krytos project]], they were ready to resort to violence. A group of its members attacked [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] agent [[Gavin Darklighter]], unaware of his true identity and thinking him an [[Humanocentrism|anti-Alien]] bigot and working for Derricote. Eventually, they were convinced of their mistake and released him.

The Combine never endorsed terrorism and its members were only lightly armed, and they became easy prey for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] security forces when they eventually found and attacked their base. Years later, [[Nolaa_Tarkona|Tarkona]] reflected that they had been weak and inferior to her own Alliance; their failure to be ruthless had been what had doomed them. The Combine would go on to help in the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|recapture of Coruscant]].

